        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Pell Flexibility Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education to implement a demonstration program allowing institutions of higher education to award job training Pell Grants to students in approved short-term career and technical education programs. </p>]]></text>
